{"tid":852664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際刑警主席失蹤 中紀委：違法受查","createTime":"2018-10-08T04:24:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T04:47:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"516091a0214897be922416dfa7a9d20abd9702b8","tid":852664,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:24:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181008/20517290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F20517290&d=GnYOVBWD5ThRqoI9%2BJHumTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7b872bc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F20517290&h=4695b440\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181008/20517290</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月08日 <br />\n<br />\n國際刑警主席失蹤<br />\n中紀委：違法受查<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181008/large/a18a01a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181008%2Flarge%2Fa18a01a.gif&h=b1d4c4d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中紀委沒詳細交代孟宏偉涉及的罪名。<br />\n資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國際刑警組織主席兼中國公安部副部長孟宏偉（64歲）返國後離奇失蹤，事件引起國際輿論關注。現居法國里昂的孟妻昨日現身，公開向國際社會求救後，中紀委隨即在深夜發佈消息稱，孟宏偉涉嫌違法受查，接受國家監委監察調查，但沒有詳細交代孟涉及的罪名。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181008/large/a18a01b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181008%2Flarge%2Fa18a01b.gif&h=3f5bc331&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n孟宏偉妻向國際社會求救<br />\n<br />\n孟宏偉自9月29日離開里昂的國際刑警總部返國後，音訊全無，居於法國里昂的孟妻無法與他聯絡，於是在10月5日在當地報案，事件引起國際輿論關注。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社昨晚引述孟妻表示，丈夫失蹤前曾寄給她一張利刀的照片，疑似是暗示自己有危險，國際刑警組織昨正式向中國當局要求給予解釋。<br />\n<br />\n孟妻更在當地時間昨日傍晚，於里昂舉行新聞發佈會，正式向國際社會求救，她亦因安全考慮，背對攝影機，沒有面對鏡頭。法國表示已經立案調查，由國際刑警組織所在地里昂警署列案調查。到了昨晚深夜，中紀委終發佈孟被調查的聲明。<br />\n<br />\n孟宏偉一直被視為中共前政治局常委周永康的派系人馬，周現時已落馬入獄，樹倒猢猻散，孟的仕途已越顯不妙。去年12月，孟先後被摘去了中國國家海洋局副局長及中國海警局局長兩職，揭開被削權的序幕。<br />\n<br />\n到今年年初，他接連缺席多個公安部重要會議，兩會後更被免去公安部黨委委員一職。孟在2016年11月當選國際刑警組織主席，任期到2020年，是首個擔任該職位的中國人。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/美聯社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n崇拜康熙毛澤東　16歲借3萬全職炒股<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n面對死亡威脅「不能退」　崔永元狠批馮小剛"},{"pid":"60d02c9e879f68d9d6b176a39ea21a744cb10836","tid":852664,"uid":207087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:27:53.000Z","msg":"Interpol 根本是腦袋有問題，大陸清官萬中無一，整件身有屎去做主席，為了媚共"},{"pid":"f0d786f6c7c4af2e191fc63d0f361bc28d33bdb3","tid":852664,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:42:03.000Z","msg":"中紀委唔係淨係查黨員架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf57b22386bc0f7ee454f2378ad29d2039d9405","tid":852664,"uid":183178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60d02c9e879f68d9d6b176a39ea21a744cb10836","tid":852664,"uid":207087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:27:53.000Z","msg":"Interpol 根本是腦袋有問題，大陸清官萬中無一，整件身有屎去做主席，為了媚共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:42:43.000Z","msg":"懷疑係輪席先有得做"},{"pid":"889dee87e41e6037a0fdbc48709a45fd427d2cf2","tid":852664,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0d786f6c7c4af2e191fc63d0f361bc28d33bdb3","tid":852664,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:42:03.000Z","msg":"中紀委唔係淨係查黨員架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:47:44.000Z","msg":"國家監察委員會"}]}